Name: Nightmarket Token
AttributesDescription: A black-gold metallic token that the Gilded Nightmarket accepts in exchange for all sorts of items.
BgDescription: A chip found in Black Alley. Some say it is cast from the daggers of the defeated, while others say it is made from violently pried-off bottle caps... In any case, it's worth something to Black Alley merchants.
